<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 12:22:09 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>文件显示，拜登2024年吊销了中国华为的8张许可证</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-revoked-8-licenses-chinas-huawei-2024-document-shows-2024-07-02/</link><description>路透社看到的一份文件显示，拜登政府今年吊销了八项允许一些公司向中国电信设备巨头华为运送货物的许可证，试图向这家复兴的公司施压。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 12:06:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-revoked-8-licenses-chinas-huawei-2024-document-shows-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪与法国艾文斯建立欧洲合作伙伴关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-forms-european-partnership-with-frances-ayvens-2024-07-02/</link><description>法国兴业银行的汽车租赁部门艾文斯与中国电动汽车公司比亚迪周二宣布建立欧洲市场合作伙伴关系。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 12:01:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-forms-european-partnership-with-frances-ayvens-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>独家：消息人士称，京东是英国包裹公司 Evri 的可能竞购者之一</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/jdcom-among-possible-bidders-british-parcel-company-evri-sources-say-2024-07-02/</link><description>两位知情人士表示，中国在线零售商京东已成为探索潜在竞购英国包裹递送公司 Evri 的几家公司之一。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:49:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/jdcom-among-possible-bidders-british-parcel-company-evri-sources-say-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾称将“毫不留情”地保护南海利益</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-says-be-relentless-protecting-interests-south-china-sea-2024-07-02/</link><description>菲律宾外交部周二表示，菲律宾告诉中国，它将“坚持不懈”保护其利益，维护其在南海的主权、主权权利和管辖权。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:06:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippine-says-be-relentless-protecting-interests-south-china-sea-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>Polestar 亏损，计划采取措施抵消中国制造电动汽车的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/polestar-posts-loss-plans-steps-offset-tariffs-china-made-evs-2024-07-02/</link><description>电动汽车（EV）制造商 Polestar 周二公布第一季度运营亏损，表示将不得不采取措施抵消欧盟和美国对其中国制造的电动汽车征收的高额进口关税。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 11:04:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/polestar-posts-loss-plans-steps-offset-tariffs-china-made-evs-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>拯救苏格兰唯一的炼油厂是英国大选中罕见的共识</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/saving-scotlands-only-refinery-rare-point-agreement-uk-election-race-2024-07-02/</link><description>参加英国大选的苏格兰所有主要政党的候选人正在向能源公司 Petroineos 施加压力，要求其推迟关闭位于格兰奇茅斯的苏格兰唯一炼油厂并挽救就业机会。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 10:25:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/uk/saving-scotlands-only-refinery-rare-point-agreement-uk-election-race-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：鲍威尔在葡萄牙经济增长放缓，曲线陡峭</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-02/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 10:06:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>NTB机构报告称，挪威公民因涉嫌为中国从事间谍活动而被捕</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/norwegian-citizen-arrested-alleged-spying-china-ntb-agency-reports-2024-07-02/</link><description>当地通讯社 NTB 周二援引挪威警察安全局 (PST) 的报道称，一名挪威公民周一因涉嫌“可能使中国受益”的间谍活动而被捕。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:35:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/norwegian-citizen-arrested-alleged-spying-china-ntb-agency-reports-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>特斯拉 6 月中国制造电动汽车销量同比下降 24.2%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-june-china-made-ev-sales-down-242-yy-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国乘用车协会(CPCA)周二的数据显示，特斯拉6月份中国制造的电动汽车销量同比下降24.2%至71,007辆。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 09:00:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/teslas-june-china-made-ev-sales-down-242-yy-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国和澳大利亚在太平洋影响力竞赛中捐赠建筑物和机场</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-australia-donate-buildings-airstrips-pacific-influence-race-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国在瓦努阿图捐赠了一座总统大楼，澳大利亚和新西兰则在邻国所罗门群岛斥资 5500 万澳元落成机场，以争夺在太平洋岛屿地区的影响力。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 08:58:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-australia-donate-buildings-airstrips-pacific-influence-race-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>律师称，外国法官之争损害了香港商法中心的吸引力</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-commercial-law-hub-allure-damaged-by-foreign-judges-row-lawyers-say-2024-07-02/</link><description>一些律师和专家表示，中国统治的香港最高法院两名英国法官的辞职不仅引发了人们对法治的担忧，还将进一步削弱人们对香港更广泛的商业法律部门的信心。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 06:04:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-commercial-law-hub-allure-damaged-by-foreign-judges-row-lawyers-say-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>由于中国经济放缓，法国餐饮公司索迪斯第三季度销售预期落后</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/french-catering-group-sodexo-lags-q3-sales-expectations-2024-07-02/</link><description>法国食品餐饮供应商索迪斯周二报告称，季度销售增长放缓，未达到市场预期，理由是中国经济放缓以及确认澳大利亚大型项目收入的方式发生了变化。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 05:11:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/french-catering-group-sodexo-lags-q3-sales-expectations-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>中国比亚迪电动汽车季度销量增长 21%，缩小与特斯拉的差距</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-posts-21-jump-quarterly-ev-sales-closes-gap-with-tesla-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国比亚迪第二季度电动汽车销量增长 21%，在第一季度将全球最大电动汽车供应商头衔拱手让给美国竞争对手特斯拉后，缩小了与特斯拉的差距。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 05:06:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-byd-posts-21-jump-quarterly-ev-sales-closes-gap-with-tesla-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>解说：中国计划制定的金融稳定法是什么？它将如何运作？</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/what-is-chinas-planned-financial-stability-law-how-will-it-work-2024-07-02/</link><description>中国即将公布其金融稳定法，其中包括设立一个基金来救助陷入困境的金融机构，这是北京为防止世界第二大经济体发生系统性金融风险而采取的更广泛努力的一部分。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 04:57:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/what-is-chinas-planned-financial-stability-law-how-will-it-work-2024-07-02/</guid></item><item><title>大型开发商销售降幅收窄后，中国房地产企业大幅上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-property-firms-jump-after-big-developers-show-smaller-sales-drop-2024-07-02/</link><description>私人数据显示，6 月份中国主要房地产开发商的销售额跌幅继续收窄，周二在香港上市的中国房地产公司股价大幅上涨。</description><pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 04:29:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-property-firms-jump-after-big-developers-show-smaller-sales-drop-2024-07-02/</guid></item></channel></rss>